1. cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper is about a conversation system that involves natural language processing and generation. 
2. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper proposes a novel approach to improve the performance of a conversation system using AI techniques. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper proposes a reranking algorithm to enable rich interaction between conversation context and candidate replies. 
4. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is relevant as the paper involves retrieving and ranking candidate replies. 
5. cs.SD (Sound) is less likely but still possible as the paper may involve audio processing for speech recognition and synthesis in the conversation system.
